   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Opportunity of Confidence. I Care!</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">I-Care plans to train and empower 2,500 Community Health Workers in three counties in Western Kenya. Millions of girls and women miss 5 days school and work every month due to their menses. Pads are not available and money is lacking to buy them. Besides that, there is a huge taboo surrounding menses; &apos;the Red Visitors&apos;.  Community Health Workers will reach out to neglected areas, sensitize girls and women about menstrual hygiene management, break the silence and provide re-usable sanitary pads</narrative>
  </description>
